indicating that theory may be empty. It looks like a topological  
theory of Witten type but it clearly depends
on the local structure of the space-time. In topological theories
there are no local degrees of freedom from the start while here we
have positive and negative norm states before introducing the ghost
fields. The requirement that the physical states are in the cohomology
of the BRST charge means that all of them, except the vacuum, appear
in zero norm combinations as we will show.  

